          <h1>Membership & Registration</h1>
          <div>
              <p><b>What does it mean to become a member?</b></p>
              <p>Becoming a member allows you to participate in surveys. You'll receive regular invitations to complete surveys based on your profile.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>How do I join?</b></p>
              <p>Click "Join Now" and complete the registration form. Verify your email to finalize your registration.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>Is registration free?</b></p>
              <p>Yes, registration is completely free. </p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>Can I sign up using my social media accounts?</b></p>
              <p>Yes, you can register using your Facebook or Google account.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>How can I edit my personal information?</b></p>
              <p>Log in, go to "General", and update your information.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>How do I delete my account?</b></p>
              <p>Log in, go to security settings, and choose "Delete Account." Alternatively, you can email us for assistance.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>I didn’t receive a verification email. What should I do?</b></p>
              <p>Check your spam folder or log in to resend the verification email.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>I forgot my password. How can I reset it?</b></p>
              <p>Click "Forgot your Password" on the login page, enter your email, and follow the instructions to reset your password.</p>
          </div><br><br>
          
          <h1>Participating in Surveys</h1>
          <div>
              <p><b>How do I participate in surveys?</b></p>
              <p>Complete your profile and verify your email. You’ll receive survey invitations via email or see them in your Survey Center.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>Why was the survey full when I just got the invitation?</b></p>
              <p>Surveys can fill up quickly. If this happens, try again with another survey invitation.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>How long does it take to complete a survey?</b></p>
              <p>Survey duration varies but typically takes around 10 minutes.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>Why don’t I qualify for some surveys?</b></p>
              <p>Some surveys target specific groups. Completing your profile increases your chances of qualifying for more surveys.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>Why haven’t I received any survey invitations?</b></p>
              <p>Ensure our emails aren’t in your spam folder. Completing your profile surveys can increase your chances of receiving invitations.</p>
          </div><br><br>
          
           
          
          <h1>Privacy & Data Protection</h1>
          <div>
              <p><b>How is my information used?</b></p>
              <p>Your data is used to match you with surveys that fit your profile. All responses are anonymized and used solely for research purposes.</p>
          </div><br>
          <div>
              <p><b>Can I control my data?</b></p>
              <p>Yes, you can modify your data or opt-out at any time by logging into your account.</p>
          </div><br>
